-- Greece Needs to Reform for Support, Westerwelle Tells Spiegel
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2012-02-11T17:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-11/greece-needs-to-reform-for-support-westerwelle-tells-spiegel.html
Greece  needs to implement reforms to
gain German support, Foreign Minister  Guido Westerwelle  said,
according to  Der Spiegel .  It is the “clear goal” to keep Greece in the euro, the
Hamburg-based news magazine cited the German minister as saying
in an e-mailed summary of an article.  To contact the reporter on this story:
